===Transfers=== The Blue Hens received three transfer students prior to the start of the 2007 season in defensive end [[Ronald Talley]] from [[Notre Dame Fighting Irish football|Notre Dame]], linebacker Johnathon Smith from [[Connecticut Huskies football|Connecticut]], and running back Jerry Butler from [[Wisconsin Badgers football|Wisconsin]].<ref name="Signing Day"/> Talley left Notre Dame midway through the [[2006 Notre Dame Fighting Irish football team|2006 season]] before transferring to Delaware.<ref>{{cite news |author=Rothstein, Michael |title=Lost in transition at Notre Dame |url=http://www.journalgazette.net/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20070824/SPORTS/708240314&SearchID=73291666340574 |work=[[The Journal Gazette]] |date=August 24, 2007 |accessdate=2010-11-19}}</ref> On August 27, offensive tackle Anthony Grosso transferred from [[Florida State Seminoles football|Florida State]] after leaving the squad a week prior.<ref>{{cite news |author=Borzello, Jeff |title=Seminole transfer plays well with Hens |url=http://www.cstv.com/sports/m-footbl/uwire/091107ack.html |work=[[CSTV]] |date=September 11, 2007 |accessdate=2010-11-20}}</ref>
